modules.description: Provides functions for validating, encoding, and decoding UTF-8 byte sequences, including checks for malformed input and conversion between byte arrays and strings. Operates on byte arrays, strings, and individual code points. Used to ensure data integrity when processing text from untrusted sources or handling binary data with embedded Unicode.

Converts between UTF-8, UTF-16, and Unicode code points, handling surrogate pairs and malformed sequences. Operates on byte strings, sequences of integers, and custom Unicode character types. Enables precise manipulation of Java-compatible Unicode strings for encoding, decoding, and traversal.
